text: Madge Sinclair (April 28, 1938 - December 20, 1995) was a character actress. She did voices for many movies. She was born in Kingston, Jamaica. She died in Los Angeles, California due to leukemia. ==References== Category:Jamaican entertainers Category:Deaths from leukemia Category:Movie actors Category:1938 births Category:1995 deaths
